### Test Related Products API

# Lấy sản phẩm liên quan (mặc định 8 sản phẩm)
GET http://localhost:3000/products/{{productId}}/related
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Lấy 6 sản phẩm liên quan
GET http://localhost:3000/products/{{productId}}/related?limit=6
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Lấy 4 sản phẩm liên quan
GET http://localhost:3000/products/{{productId}}/related?limit=4
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Test với ID không hợp lệ
GET http://localhost:3000/products/invalid-id/related
Content-Type: application/json

